{{wiktionary|Buffalo|buffalo|buffaloe|buffaloes|buffalos}}
'''Buffalo''' (or '''buffaloe''') may refer to:
{{tocright}}

==Animals==
* [[African buffalo]] or Cape Buffalo (''Syncerus caffer'')
* [[American bison]] (''Bison bison''), also commonly known as the American buffalo
* [[European bison]] (''Bison bonasus'')
* ''[[Bubalus]]'', a genus of bovines including various water buffalo species
* [[Water buffalo]]
* [[Italian buffalo]] or Italian Mediterranean buffalo

